<P>Give your orders in a plain di&s;tinct manner, with good-nature joined to a &s;teadine&s;s that will &s;hew they mu&s;t be punctually obeyed. Treat all your dome&s;tics with &s;uch mildne&s;s and affability, that you may be &s;erved rather out of affection <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> fear. Let them live happily under you. Give them lei&s;ure for their own bu&s;ine&s;s. <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> for innocent recreation, and more e&s;pecially <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word">
